      "content": "GSAP ScrollTrigger Config\n\n• snap: 1 / (sections.length - 1)\n• scrub: 1\n• pin: true per section\n• ease: 'power3.inOut'\n• Theme toggle: gsap.to(root, { cssVars })\n• Duration: 0.6s crossfade"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "1jTJK",
      "x": 1550,
      "y": 220,
      "name": "GSAP — Hero",
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "content": "Hero Animations\n\n• title: splitText + stagger 0.03s\n• tagline: fadeIn + y:30, delay 0.4s\n• CTAs: fadeIn + y:20, delay 0.6s\n• image: scale(1.1→1) + opacity, 1.2s"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "b7zQq",
      "x": 1550,
      "y": 380,
      "name": "GSAP — Slide Transitions",
      "width": 300,
      "height": 140,
      "content": "Slide Transitions\n\n• Enter: clipPath circle(0% → 100%)\n• Content: stagger fadeIn + y:40px\n• Section labels: typewriter effect\n• Dot nav: scale pulse on active\n• Duration: 0.8s per slide\n• Easing: power4.out"
    },
