      "x": 1550,
      "y": 560,
      "name": "GSAP — Theme Toggle",
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "content": "Theme Toggle Animation\n\n• gsap.to(':root', { duration: 0.5 })\n• Animate CSS custom properties\n• Toggle knob: x tween 20px\n• Background: crossfade 0.4s\n• Text: color morph 0.3s"
